  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Roderick</b> is a Westerosi given name. It may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Roderick_Blackwood\" title=\"Roderick Blackwood\">Roderick Blackwood</a>, Lord of Raventree Hall during the reign of King Arlan III Durrandon</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roderick_Dustin\" title=\"Roderick Dustin\">Roderick Dustin</a>, known as \"Roddy the Ruin\", Lord of Barrowton and head of House Dustin during the Dance of the Dragons</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roderick_Stark\" title=\"Roderick Stark\">Roderick Stark</a>, a Lord of Winterfell and head of House Stark</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roderick&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik\" title=\"Rodrik\">Rodrik</a> (disambiguation)</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404060747\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:38654-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404060747 and revision id 323575\n -->\n",
